comments: Harden (HOU) places a hand to the front of Batum's (CHA) chest that affects his SQBR and ability to maintain control of the ball.
Batum (CHA) touched the ball simultaneously as it hits the backboard.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gordon (HOU) and the two make incidental contact as they disengage.
Harden (HOU) makes incidental contact to the arm of Lamb (CHA) after the release that does not affect his follow-through.
Walker (CHA) makes contact to the ball, any additional contact to Harden's (HOU) arm is deemed incidental.
Walker (CHA) has a resting hand and does not extend it into Harden's (HOU) body on his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Zeller (CHA) is firming and makes marginal contact with Paul (HOU) on his pick.
Capela (HOU) makes incidental contact to the body of Walker (CHA) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Walker (CHA) at the start of his drive.
Zeller (CHA) makes contact to the body of Harden (HOU) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes contact to the body of Walker (CHA) at the end of the drive but the contact is marginal.
Capela (HOU) makes incidental contact to the body of Lamb (CHA) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Lamb (CHA) slides his pivot foot.
Zeller (CHA) extends his arms and continues to move into Capela's (HOU) path while setting the screen.
Williams (CHA) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Zeller (CHA) makes marginal contact with Paul (HOU) as he sets the screen during the inbound.
[Observable in enhanced video] Walker (CHA) shuffles his feet after his gather.
Capela (HOU) clamps Zeller's (CHA) arm during the rebound and restricts his ability to gather the loose ball.
